OL,3,CCelebrations in Rory's hometown with
OL,4,Cback-to-back win in Masters
OL,6,FThere were scenes of jubilation in
OL,7,FHolywood Golf Club in County Down as
OL,8,FRory McIlroy claimed his second
OL,9,FMasters title in Augusta.
OL,11,FMcIlroy's hometown Golf Club in County
OL,12,FDown erupted in cheers as he tapped in
OL,13,Fa putt to win by one on 12-under-par
OL,14,Fat Augusta National.
OL,16,FThe 36-year-old became the fourth man
OL,17,Fto win consecutive Masters titles,
OL,18,Fhaving first secured the green jacket
OL,19,F` and career grand slam ` last year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
