OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776272750
OL,3,CCelebrations in Rory's hometown with
OL,4,Cback-to-back win in Masters
OL,6,FAmid chants of "Rory, Rory, Rory",
OL,7,Fspirits were high with the bar serving
OL,8,FMasters-themed cocktails ` including a
OL,9,F"Rory's Green Jacket" with Irish gin,
OL,10,FBelfast elderflower cordial, lime and
OL,11,Fsoda.
OL,13,FSix clear on Friday night, what could
OL,14,Fhave been a procession was anything
OL,15,Fbut for McIlroy. The final round was
OL,16,Ftypical McIlroy, who looked to be
OL,17,Fplaying himself out of it on the front
OL,18,Fnine before rallying with a series of
OL,19,Fbirdies.
OL,26,@nD@POUnD@aO]qD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
