OL,3,CCelebrations in Rory's hometown with
OL,4,Cback-to-back win in Masters
OL,6,FAt the Clubhouse, Sullivan Upper
OL,7,FSchool, where McIlroy studied, was
OL,8,Frepresented among those cheering on.
OL,10,FSpeaking to the Press Association at
OL,11,FHolywood Golf Club, 19-year-old Zach
OL,12,FWoods said he and his friends thought
OL,13,Fthe victory was "really inspiring".
OL,15,FHe said: "It is great to be honest, to
OL,16,Fsee a boy from our community achieve
OL,17,Fsuch great things.
OL,19,F"It pushes us to strive to do the best
OL,20,Fthat we can to achieve the things that
OL,21,Fwe love."
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@bO]wD@JOU{D@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
