OL,3,CCelebrations in Rory's hometown with
OL,4,Cback-to-back win in Masters
OL,6,FHamish Johnson, 18, said he "never
OL,7,Fdoubted" McIlroy, adding: "He's got
OL,8,Fthe potential to be the best ever."
OL,10,FCelebrating the win, Leah James said:
OL,11,F"it was just fantastic" to watch along
OL,12,Fat Holywood ` having had to sneakily
OL,13,Ftry and keep up with the action while
OL,14,Fon night shift last year.
OL,16,FMs James, from Bangor and a member at
OL,17,FHolywood, said McIlroy brought a lot
OL,18,Fof interest to the club.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@HO]oD@[OUpD@cO]sD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
