OL,3,CCelebrations in Rory's hometown with
OL,4,Cback-to-back win in Masters
OL,6,FShe said the back-to-back wins were
OL,7,F"incredible", reflecting: "He was just
OL,8,Fso calm and so collected this year and
OL,9,Fseeing him do it made my day ` just
OL,10,Fhappy for him."
OL,12,FBack at Augusta, an emotional McIlroy
OL,13,Fthanked those in Holywood for their
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]oD@[OUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
