PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776272750
OL,3,CCelebrations in Rory's hometown with
OL,4,Cback-to-back win in Masters
OL,6,FAsked for his message to those
OL,7,Fwatching at home during the green
OL,8,Fjacket presentation, he said: "I was a
OL,9,Flittle kid with a dream and the
OL,10,Fsupport that I had from my family,
OL,11,Ffriends and everyone back at home `
OL,12,Fsome people probably thought it was
OL,13,Foutlandish to dream the things that I
OL,14,Fwanted to do but I had amazing support
OL,15,Fback home and I can't thank them all
OL,16,Fenough for that continued support."
OL,26,@pD@_OUxD@cO]
